The Controlling Function
------------------------

   In keeping with the spirit of this example, the controlling function
is kept to the bare minimum.  The only requirement is that it call
@{b}yyparse@{ub} to start the process of parsing.

     main ()
     {
       yyparse ();
     }


@EndNode

